<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFRoe1916">Roe, Joseph Wickham (1916), <i>English and American Tool Builders</i>, New Haven, Connecticut, USA: Yale University Press, <a href="/wiki/Library_of_Congress_Control_Number" title="Library of Congress Control Number">LCCN</a> <a href="http://lccn.loc.gov/16011753" class="external text" title="http://lccn.loc.gov/16011753" rel="nofollow">16-011753</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=English+and+American+Tool+Builders&amp;rft.aulast=Roe&amp;rft.aufirst=Joseph+Wickham&amp;rft.au=Roe%2C+Joseph+Wickham&amp;rft.date=1916&amp;rft.place=New+Haven%2C+Connecticut%2C+USA&amp;rft.pub=Yale+University+Press&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Industrial_Revolution"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>. Reprinted by McGraw-Hill, New York and London, 1926 (<a href="/wiki/Library_of_Congress_Control_Number" title="Library of Congress Control Number">LCCN</a> <a href="http://lccn.loc.gov/27024075" class="external text" title="http://lccn.loc.gov/27024075" rel="nofollow">27-024075</a>); and by Lindsay Publications, Inc., Bradley, IL, USA (<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780917914737" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-917914-73-7</a>). Also <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=X-EJAAAAIAAJ&amp;printsec=titlepage" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=X-EJAAAAIAAJ&amp;printsec=titlepage" rel="nofollow">available online</a> via Google Book Search.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Vaclav Smil; <i>Energy in World History.</i> Westview Press, 1994 <a href="http://www.questia.com/PM.qst?a=o&amp;d=94468450" class="external text" title="http://www.questia.com/PM.qst?a=o&amp;d=94468450" rel="nofollow">online edition</a></li>
